mouse_filter = 2
theme_override_colors/default_color = Color(0, 0, 0, 1)
theme_override_font_sizes/normal_font_size = 14
bbcode_enabled = true
text = "Hello Dave !

Just a quick reminder to please make sure that all equipment is put back in its place after use.

Especially the [i]prototype[/i] plugin. Seriously Dave, this thing should ABSOLUTELY not be laying around unattended like last week. 

I will have to report further infractions. 

Thank you for your attention to this matter.
Have a good week end.

Eric Eccert
Executive Operational Manager"
scroll_active = false

